verbose_text: To study the electronic structures of 1 to 8 in detail, gas phase structures and natural bond orbital (NBO) analyses were calculated using density functional theory (DFT) with the Gaussian program package18 at the B3LYP LANL2DZ level of theory.19 While the charge of the phenoxide oxygen atom in both type of complexes (1 0.98, 2 0.96, 3 0.96, 4 0.95; 5 0.97, 6 0.95, 7 0.95, 8 0.95) is almost identical, compounds 1 and 5 show the highest values.
